📌 Asset-X Mini Banking System

Overview

Asset-X is a mini banking system built using Node.js, Express, MongoDB, and JWT authentication. This system allows users to register, login, create bank accounts, deposit, withdraw, and check balances.

🚀 Installation & Setup

1️⃣ Clone the Repository

  git clone https://github.com/decency07/Asset-x-a-mini-bank.git
  cd asset-x-banking
  cd code

2️⃣ Install Dependencies

  install Node.js, MongoDB, Postman or Thunder Client ( for VS Code )

3️⃣ Set Up Environment Variables

Create a .env file in the project root 

4️⃣ Start the Server

    node index.js

If successful, you should see:

🚀 Server running on PORT_NUMBER
✅ Connected to MongoDB


🛠 Tools & Technologies

Backend: Node.js, Express.js

Database: MongoDB

Authentication: JWT (JSON Web Token)

API Testing: Thunder Client / Postman



Developed by P. MURALI

